<p><h2>The Life of Bernie</h2></p>
<p><h2> Early Life </h2></p>

Born September 8, 1941 <br>

<h2>Education 1959-1964 </h2>
<p>Brooklyn College</p>
<p>University of Chicago</p>

<h2>Activism 1962-1963</h2>
<p>Led a rally as a member of Student Nonviolent Coordinating Committee</p>
<p>Attended  Martin Luther King Jr's. March on Washington</p>

<h2>Political Career 1971- </h2>
<p>Mayor of Burlington 1981-1988</p>
<p>Congressman 1991-2006</p>
<p>Senator of Vermont 2006-</p> 
<p>Presidential Candidate 2015-</p>
